EU May Extend Kyoto Climate Treaty if Conditions Are ’Right’

-- B y   [ b n : P R S N = 1 6 0 6 8 0 7 0 ]   D a n i e l   T e n   K a t e   [ ]   a n d   [ b n : P R S N = 1 6 5 0 2 7 1 9 ]   C a t h e r i n e   A i r l i e   [ ]
